  "title": "Project-Based Content Writer (remote) ✍️ $15 Per Article",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Hiring: Project-Based Content Writer (Remote) ✍️ ($15 per article)</strong><br /></p><p>We’re looking for a <strong>project-based content writer</strong> to support us in writing high-quality articles for our website, focused on education-related topics.<br /></p><p><strong>Scope of work</strong></p><p> • Write articles for our website (topics and briefs will be provided)</p><p> • Ensure content is clear, engaging, and well-structured</p><p> • Adapt writing style to suit our brand tone<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p> • Strong command of <strong>well-written English</strong></p><p> • Familiar with the <strong>Singapore education syllabus</strong></p><p> • <strong>Singaporean preferred</strong></p><p> • Self-disciplined and able to work independently — we won’t micromanage, but <strong>deadlines must be met</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Role details</strong></p><p> • Project-based engagement</p><p> • Flexible working arrangement</p><p> • Paid per project / per article</p>",
